<DOCID> 307472 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 14, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 5; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
