<P>
Justice for All: "Equal Justice," the gritty, Emmy-winning series about life in 
a big-city prosecutor's office, will replace "Cop Rock" Wednesdays at 10 p.m. 
on ABC beginning Jan. 9, the network announced Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
