-- RUSSIA; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN POLICY -- USSR; LEADERSHIP; USSR -- 
GOVERNMENT; USSR -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; GOVERNMENT REFORM; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL 
S; YELTSIN, BORIS N 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
