Angeles reserve combat unit to be called up in the Persian Gulf crisis. Members 
-- reporting to the Pasadena Marine Reserve Center, above -- spent the last few 
days getting ready; about 10 in the platoon have gotten married in the past 
week. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
